episodes.title: PNP INSPECTS UNDERGROUND ROOMS AT KOJC COMPOUND
episodes.description:
WATCH: An EXCLUSIVE footage shows the Philippine National Police (PNP) inspecting underground rooms at a mansion inside the Kingdom of Jesus Christ (KOJC) Compound. Among these is a room allegedly linked to Alias "Amanda", the whistleblower accusing Pastor Apollo C. Quiboloy of sexual exploitation. Alias Amanda's Senate testimony has been key in the ongoing investigation. | via Jasper Dawang
